+3. [P1] Fix A and Fix C are absent, so there is no session ground truth to support the reopened-table split — the current file contains zero hits for `openSessions`, `openSessionByTableId`, `staleTime: 5_000`, `maybeTableIdOrCompositeKey`, or `orphanInvalidateSigRef`, and it jumps from the requests error handling block straight into `lastUpdatedAt` around `pages/StaffOrdersMobile/staffordersmobile.jsx:3527`. FIX: restore the `openSessions` `useQuery`, rebuild `openSessionByTableId`, set its `staleTime` to `5_000`, and add the orphan-detection `useEffect` after that memo exactly as specified in Fix A and Fix C.
