2. [P1] The session-aware consumers from Fix B.2-B.6 are also missing: `filteredGroups`/`tabCounts`, banner navigation, live `data-group-id`, and the rendered card `key`/expand/highlight state still use `group.id` instead of a composite session key. See [staffordersmobile.jsx](C:/Users/ASUS/Dev/Menu AI Cowork/menuapp-code-review/pages/StaffOrdersMobile/staffordersmobile.jsx:3829) and [staffordersmobile.jsx](C:/Users/ASUS/Dev/Menu AI Cowork/menuapp-code-review/pages/StaffOrdersMobile/staffordersmobile.jsx:4102).
3. [P1] Fix A and Fix C are absent: there is no `openSessions` query, no `openSessionByTableId`, no `staleTime: 5_000`, and no orphan invalidation effect, so the page has no session ground truth to detect reopened tables promptly.

